1.title: Performance Anxiety

episode of.title: Elle and Tito: The Married Life (TV Series 2010– )

1.plot: "Marital Relations": - The newlyweds are living together as husband and wife and there are a number of adjustments they need to make. Elle isn't happy about the quality of the sex, while Tito must come to grips with the cooking, cleaning and shopping roles.

2.title: Baby Talk

episode of.title: Elle and Tito: The Married Life (TV Series 2010– )

2.plot: A trip home to Pennsylvania is the back-drop for Elle and Tito to have the age old debate...when is the right time to start having kids? Elle is eager but Tito is convinced that they are not ready.

3.title: A Pound of Flesh

episode of.title: Elle and Tito: The Married Life (TV Series 2010– )

3.plot: Elle and Tito decide it's time to get back in shape. What starts out as a joint effort turns into a heated competition to decide who can lose more weight.

4.title: Sleepless in North Hollywood

episode of.title: Elle and Tito: The Married Life (TV Series 2010– )

4.plot: Tito's insomnia has reached a point where it's beginning to affect the marriage. The search for a cure leads to hypnotists and a sleep clinic.

5.title: Operation Big Bear

episode of.title: Elle and Tito: The Married Life (TV Series 2010– )

5.plot: For Elle's birthday, Tito plans a surprise trip to the famed ski resort. But Elle's expectations for a romantic weekend are squashed when it turns out Tito has invited all his friends to stay in the cabin as well.

6.title: Big Bear 2: The Wrath of Tito

episode of.title: Elle and Tito: The Married Life (TV Series 2010– )

6.plot: Once Tito realizes Elle fooled him with an elaborate practical joke, he plots his revenge using the couple's six month anniversary as the bait.

7.title: Stage Fright

episode of.title: Elle and Tito: The Married Life (TV Series 2010– )

7.plot: Elle and Tito get their music careers back in gear, but Tito's stage fright is standing in their way. Tito attempts to cure himself by performing at a comedy club.

8.title: Putting It on Wax

episode of.title: Elle and Tito: The Married Life (TV Series 2010– )

8.plot: While hard at work writing a love song, Elle gets upset at Tito for asking her to get a bikini wax. She agrees to do it only if Tito gets one as well. This challenge sends Tito on a mission to free himself from his fears.

9.title: Elle & Tito Live

episode of.title: Elle and Tito: The Married Life (TV Series 2010– )

9.plot: The next step in the Elle and Tito music career is to do a live show and work on their stage presence. Elle arranges a meeting with a stage director and Tito enlists in an improvisation class.

10.title: Old Folks Phobia

episode of.title: Elle and Tito: The Married Life (TV Series 2010– )

10.plot: Elle and Tito argue about doing charity work. Elle responds by signing them both up to do volunteer work at an Old Folks home and Tito must face his fear of the elderly.
